text: Fallen Leaves () is a 2023 Finnish-German comedy drama movie directed by Aki Kaurismäki and is the continuation of the trilogy series by Proletariat series. It stars Alma Pöysti, Jussi Vatanen, Janne Hyytiäinen, Nuppu Koivu, Matti Onnismaa and Simon Al-Bazoon. ==Other websites== * Category:2023 comedy movies Category:2023 drama movies Category:2020s comedy-drama movies Category:Finnish movies Category:German comedy movies Category:German drama movies Category:Movies set in Helsinki Category:Movies directed by Aki Kaurismäki
